org.jboss.windup.ast.java.data

Class ClassReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.windup.ast.java.data.ClassReference
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnotationClassReference

    public class ClassReference
extends Object
    Contains a name that has been referenced by the Java source file. This can include the qualified name (for example, com.example.data.Foo) as well as information about the reference. Information includes indicating where the reference was found within the file (line, column, and length) as well as how it was used (import, method call, etc).
    Author:
    Jesse Sightler
